293
00:17:22,670 --> 00:17:24,079
Great!

294
00:17:24,119 --> 00:17:26,349
It's finally over.

295
00:17:26,480 --> 00:17:27,980
Let all the ridicule

296
00:17:28,020 --> 00:17:29,260
vanish

297
00:17:29,290 --> 00:17:31,760
with my memory.

298
