339
00:19:32,230 --> 00:19:35,310
We just wanted to give you a pleasant surprise.

340
00:19:36,790 --> 00:19:38,920
But it's a terrible surprise!

341
00:19:41,010 --> 00:19:42,270
We heard the nurse say

342
00:19:42,270 --> 00:19:43,710
