513
00:27:45,440 --> 00:27:46,270
Nan Hua.

514
00:27:47,050 --> 00:27:50,320
What's your grandfather's name?

515
00:27:53,460 --> 00:27:54,550
It's Nan Hua, too.

516
00:27:56,840 --> 00:28:00,900
Mr. Nan Hua, is your grandpa still alive?

517
00:28:07,250 --> 00:28:08,240
